timeline.bodyText:
The beauty of having builder pattern is to avoid this massive change when adding a new field. I suggest that we make lastUpdateTime as an optional here. We can give lastUpdateTime a default value and only set the lastUpdateTime when it's not the default value.
public ContainerBuilder(short id, String name, ContainerStatus status, String description, short parentAccountId) {
    this.id = id;
    this.name = name;
    this.status = status;
    this.description = description;
    this.parentAccountId = parentAccountId;
}

public ContainerBuilder lastUpdateTime(long val) {
    this.lastUpdateTime = val;
    return this;
}

