this is a bad signature in builder. It should be
public ContainerBuilder lastUpdateTime(long val) {
    this.lastUpdateTime = val;
    return this;
}

It's up to you to prefix set to the method name. I would not, but to keep it consistent with all the methods in this file, we probably should.

